snippet.title: Official Nightbanes Trailer
snippet.description:
Play now for free!
English Version : http://bit.ly/GNX18a
German Version : http://bit.ly/1gEN1w1

Official trailer of the new free-to-play collectible card game Nightbanes!

Create your own deck and challenge your friends and other players around the world in impressive 3D battles! 

Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/nightbanes?ref=hl
